org.apache.juneau.assertions

Class FluentDateAssertion<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.assertions.Assertion
      • org.apache.juneau.assertions.FluentAssertion<R>
        • org.apache.juneau.assertions.FluentDateAssertion<R>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - The return type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DateAssertion

    public class FluentDateAssertion<R>
extends FluentAssertion<R>
    Used for fluent assertion calls against dates.
    Example:

    // Validates the response expiration is after the current date. client .get(URL) .run() .assertDateHeader("Expires").isAfterNow();
